rComments: Great course, learned much more than I thought I would because of his energy towards the subject. If I could, I would take it again just to learn more. He's very tough in the grading department but always gives what's deserved.
SUCH a great prof! The poor dude can't use projectors every well haaa

do not take the history by numbers class... what a pointless class... OMG!!! but he is a very nice guy,.. just can't really explain anything to do with the class... i think i knew more about the subject before i took the class..
Great man, seems to be really devoted to teaching. Can be a hard marker, and the exam was pretty tough. But nevertheless, a nice man who tries to really paint a picture of the cold war.
Johnson's a stand-up ****, looks like he just woke up everytime he comes in the door. Informative and quirky, rambles at times though.
Lovely man. His classes are fun and informative, and the info. stays with you a long time. Tall dude, totally absent-minded prof type. I took 3 courses with him. Would take 33 if I could.
His lectures are like listening to an action movie on take! I loved his class!
Looved having him as a professor! really knows his stuff
he knows so much it is incredible, i like that he gives a range of information to make a point.  My favourite prof
Soemtimes confusing and rambling, but definitely knows the subject material. Great depth of knowledge, just doesn't bring it out all of the time. Sometimes very obscure, and a hard marker.
